    "description": "Do you enjoy dungeonering in the <i>dark</i>? <br>What about when the dark is even... <i>darker</i>? <br>Then you'll love <strong>Back To The Dark</strong>!<br><br>Singleplayer medieval-fantasy extraction melee-looter with the occasional arrow and spell.<br><br>Can you survive the encroaching dark long enough to extract through a blue escape portal? Or will you be forced to delve deeper in the darkness through a red portal?<br><br>Oh and don't forget to loot some treasure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features (Demo 2)</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 Playable Classes: Soldier, Archer, Marauder, Mage, Thief, Monk<br></li><li>Multiple weapons per class, with chained attacks!<br></li><li>3 Dungeon levels!<br></li><li>Tutorial dungeon!<br></li><li>Various monster types, including spiders!<br></li><li>Armour!<br></li><li>Potions!<br></li><li>Jewellery!<br></li><li>XP, levels, attributes!<br></li><li>Treasure!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Not Yet Included</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Skills<br></li><li>Perks<br></li><li>&quot;Useful&quot; spells<br></li><li>More weapons<br></li><li>More treasure<br></li><li>More mobs!<br></li><li>More dungeons!<br></li><li>More coming soon!</li></ul>",
